      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">12.505</ph> Applicability of certain laws to contracts for the acquisition of COTS items.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
         <p id="d734e8" class="- topic/p ">COTS items are a subset of commercial items. Therefore, any laws listed in sections <xref href="12.503.dita#FAR_12_503"
                  base="i1112774"
                  outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                  class="- topic/xref ">12.503</xref> and <xref href="12.504.dita#FAR_12_504"
                  base="i1112857"
                  outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                  class="- topic/xref ">12.504</xref> are also inapplicable or modified in their applicability to contracts or subcontracts for the acquisition of COTS items. In addition, the following laws are not applicable to contracts for the acquisition of COTS items:</p>
         <ol id="d713e28" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li props="Runin" class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d740e18" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
               </p>
               <ol id="d713e38" class="- topic/ol ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d740e23" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        
								                The portion of <xref href="http://uscode.house.gov/browse.xhtml;jsessionid=114A3287C7B3359E597506A31FC855B3"
                              format="html"
                              scope="external"
                              class="- topic/xref ">41 U.S. C. 8302(a)(1)</xref>, that reads "substantially all from articles, materials, or supplies mined, produced, or manufactured, in the United States," Buy American- Supplies, component test (see <xref href="52.225-1.dita#FAR_52_225_1"
                              base="i1053372"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">52.225-1</xref> and <xref href="52.225-3.dita#FAR_52_225_3"
                              base="i1053446"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">52.225-3</xref>).</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d740e37" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        
								                The portion of <xref href="http://uscode.house.gov/browse.xhtml;jsessionid=114A3287C7B3359E597506A31FC855B3"
                              format="html"
                              scope="external"
                              class="- topic/xref ">41 U.S .C. 8303(a)(2)</xref>, that reads "substantially all from articles, materials, or supplies mined, produced, or manufactured in the United States," Buy American- Construction Materials, component test (see <xref href="52.225-9.dita#FAR_52_225_9"
                              base="i1053788"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">52.225-9</xref> and <xref href="52.225-11.dita#FAR_52_225_11"
                              base="i1054019"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">52.225-11</xref>).</p>
                  </li>
               </ol>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d740e51" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  <xref href="http://uscode.house.gov/browse.xhtml;jsessionid=114A3287C7B3359E597506A31FC855B3"
                        format="html"
                        scope="external"
                        class="- topic/xref ">42 U.S.C. 69 62(c)(3)(A)</xref>, Certification and Estimate of Percentage of Recovered Material.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d740e58" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph>
                  
						            Compliance Plan and Certification Requirement, section 1703 of the National Defense Authorization Act for Fiscal Year 2013 (Pub. L. 112-239), Title XVII, Ending trafficking in Government Contracting (see <xref href="52.222-50.dita#FAR_52_222_50"
                        base="i1056535"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.222-50</xref>(h) and <xref href="52.222-56.dita#FAR_52_222_56"
                        base="i1056889"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.222-56</xref>).</p>
            </li>
         </ol>
      </conbody>
